Problem Statement:
	Students have difficulties in understanding various math formula. It's easy to learn things but the better understood 
	the more it is perceived and good to recall. Visualizing formula enables students to perceive things better and concepts are 
	cleared more efficiently.
Solution:
	To understand things with greater efficiency and bring the concepts to practical problems is where, VISUAL MATHEMATICS FORMULA,
	comes into action. Visual mathematics formula shows the live presentation of various mathematical formula, 
	through which the students can absorb the basic concepts and visualize their graphs.
